title: Fabio & Grooverider show 05/04/2009
description:
Fabio and Grooverider Drum and Bass Show 
Sunday 5 April 2009 

Grooverider welcomes drum and bass legends Total Science into the studio, who shares jokes and go in the mix with some brand new tunes!

Rider also drops some brand new bangers from Dillinja, Zen, an exclusive from DJ Clipz, and goes head to head with Fabio in the Rewind Tracks. Who's packing the most heat this week? Find out right here!

Broadcast: BBC Radio 1, SAT.
